'Here you delete a team. It is not so easy to delete a team. You must first delete all tasks assigned to the team as well as all notifications used by the team. Then it is possible to do this delete function.' => 'Her sletter du et hold. Det er ikke så let at slette et hold. Du skal først slette alle opgaver, der er tildelt holdet, samt alle underretninger, som teamet bruger. Derefter er det muligt at udføre denne slettefunktion.',
'Here you delete a user. It is not so easy to delete a user. You must first delete all tasks assigned to the user as well as all notifications used by the user. Then it might be possible to do this delete function. Another way is to simply remove all rights for this person or you can even define the person as deleted or not active in the profile.' => 'Her sletter du en bruger. Det er ikke så let at slette en bruger. Du skal først slette alle opgaver, der er tildelt brugeren, samt alle underretninger, som brugeren bruger. Derefter er det muligvis muligt at udføre denne slettefunktion. En anden måde er blot at fjerne alle rettigheder for denne person, eller du kan endda definere personen som slettet eller ikke aktiv i profilen.',
